title.narrative: NONG SAENG NATURAL GAS POWER PROJECT

description.narrative: The Project will help (i) provide reliable and least-cost power to fuel economic growth and prevent supply shortfalls; (ii) promote efficient combined cycle technology and baseload alternatives to coal-fired generation; (iii) support public-private partnerships that enhance efficiency in the sector.
